   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>Introduction The Prayer That Expresses God's Will What Is God's Eternal Will The Son of God and Christ The Rebellion of the Angels God's Purpose in Creating Man The Fall of Man The Work of Christ The Organization, Goal, and Methods of Satan's Kingdom The Position and Responsibility of the Church</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>II.</S>
