   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>The Mystery of Christ The Body of Christ The Difference Between Being a Believer and Being a Member The Supply of the Body The Protection, Limitation, and Ministry of the Body Authority in the Body The Anointing of the Body The Order of the Body The Principle of the Body The Riches in the Body The Ministry in the Body</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>III.</S>
